Title: An Act Changing the Name of Calbay Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Santiago Mier Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 746
An Act Changing the Name of Calbay Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Santiago Mier Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Calbay Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, shall be changed to Santiago Mier Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
